remarks.format:


## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1456f-118">預設值為`value`參數使用空字串 ("")。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-118">The default for the `value` parameter uses the empty string ("").</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="1456f-119">`value`參數<xref:System.Net.Cookie>不得`null`參考 (在 Visual Basic 中 Nothing)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-119">The `value` parameter for a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> must not be a `null` reference (Nothing in Visual Basic).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1456f-120">分號 （";"） 和逗號 （"，"） 字元是保留，無法傳入`value`參數中傳遞的字串除非`value`參數用雙引號括住。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-120">The semicolon (";") and comma (",") characters are reserved and cannot be passed in the `value` parameter unless the string passed in the `value` parameter is enclosed in double quotes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1456f-121">因此下列的範例建構函式會成功，但當您嘗試加入<xref:System.Net.Cookie>至<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer>執行個體，其<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Net.Cookie)>或<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Uri,System.Net.Cookie)>方法，此作業將會失敗並擲回例外狀況：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-121">So the following example constructor would succeed, but when you try to add this <xref:System.Net.Cookie> to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance with the <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Net.Cookie)> or <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Uri,System.Net.Cookie)> methods, the operation will fail and throw an exception:</span></span>  

 ```
 System.Net.Cookie cookie = new System.Net.Cookie("contoso", "123,456");
 cookie.Domain = "https://contoso.com";
 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ```  

 <span data-ttu-id="1456f-122">不過，會建立下列建構函式逸出這些特殊字元<xref:System.Net.Cookie>可以加入至<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer>執行個體：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-122">However, the following constructor with these special characters escaped will create a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> that can be added to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance:</span></span>  

 ```
 System.Net.Cookie cookie = new System.Net.Cookie("contoso", "\"123,456\"");
 cookie.Domain = "https://contoso.com";
 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ```

 <span data-ttu-id="1456f-123">逗號字元作為分隔符號之間的同一行上的個別 cookie。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-123">The comma character is used as a delimiter between separate cookies on the same line.</span></span>



## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1456f-141">預設值為`path`參數使用空字串 ("")。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-141">The default for the `path` parameter uses the empty string ("").</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="1456f-142">`value`參數<xref:System.Net.Cookie>不得`null`參考 (在 Visual Basic 中 Nothing)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-142">The `value` parameter for a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> must not be a `null` reference (Nothing in Visual Basic).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1456f-143">分號 （";"） 和逗號 （"，"） 字元是保留，無法傳入`value`參數中傳遞的字串除非`value`參數用雙引號括住。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-143">The semicolon (";") and comma (",") characters are reserved and cannot be passed in the `value` parameter unless the string passed in the `value` parameter is enclosed in double quotes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1456f-144">因此下列的範例建構函式會成功，但當您嘗試加入<xref:System.Net.Cookie>至<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer>執行個體，其<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Net.Cookie)>或<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Uri,System.Net.Cookie)>方法，此作業將會失敗並擲回例外狀況：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-144">So the following example constructor would succeed, but when you try to add this <xref:System.Net.Cookie> to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance with the <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Net.Cookie)> or <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Uri,System.Net.Cookie)> methods, the operation will fail and throw an exception:</span></span>  

 ```
 System.Net.Cookie cookie = new System.Net.Cookie("contoso", "123,456", "");
 cookie.Domain = "https://contoso.com";
 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ```  

 <span data-ttu-id="1456f-145">不過，會建立下列建構函式逸出這些特殊字元<xref:System.Net.Cookie>可以加入至<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer>執行個體：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-145">However, the following constructor with these special characters escaped will create a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> that can be added to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance:</span></span>  

 ```
 System.Net.Cookie cookie = new System.Net.Cookie("contoso", "\"123,456\"", "");
 cookie.Domain = "https://contoso.com";
 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ``` 

 <span data-ttu-id="1456f-146">逗號字元作為分隔符號之間的同一行上的個別 cookie。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-146">The comma character is used as a delimiter between separate cookies on the same line.</span></span>



## Remarks  
