 ```  

 <span data-ttu-id="1456f-170">不過，會建立下列建構函式逸出這些特殊字元<xref:System.Net.Cookie>可以加入至<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer>執行個體：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-170">However, the following constructor with these special characters escaped will create a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> that can be added to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance:</span></span>  

