 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ```  

 <span data-ttu-id="1456f-171">逗號字元作為分隔符號之間的同一行上的個別 cookie。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1456f-171">The comma character is used as a delimiter between separate cookies on the same line.</span></span>
